      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n224\nNeeds Review\n224\n(310 on an ultra-advanced meta-abstraction (\"not 2 mothers once but one mother seen twice, at 2 times + places\" - related to Plato's recovery of the eide). There is something I must face + face fully + honestly. The messenger vision - that was (first of all) not a dream but a vision (although perhaps hypnopompic). what I must face is that it sums up + expresses absolutely, precisely + perfectly what (I discovered recently) to be t",
